;;; Fork of the builtin Generic-Event-Dispatcher, stripped down, with added delta time calculation
(define Custom-Event-Dispatcher {
  is-on: #t
  process: nil
  process-mutex: nil
  context-frame: {}
  period: 250
  repeat-limit: 0
  current-repeats: 0
  event-type: AllEventTypes
  is-disabled-event: #f

  compute-period: (lambda () period)

  compute-repeat-limit: (lambda () repeat-limit)

  run-update-side-effect: (lambda ()) ;; Optional to implement
  run-finish-side-effect: (lambda ()) ;; Optional to implement

  run: (lambda (proc)
    (let* ((dt 0.0))
      (do ((finish #f finish))
          (finish (run-finish-side-effect) (cleanup-function))
        (set! dt (time (begin
          (run-update-side-effect)
          (update-function dt)
          (set! finish (proc-sleep proc period))))))))

  create-sync: (lambda ()
    (when (nil? process-mutex)
      (process-mutex:! self (make-channel 1))))

  start: (lambda ()
    (create-sync:> self)
    (process-mutex<- nil)
    (when (nil? process)
      (process:! self (fork (lambda (p) (run:> self p)))))
    (<-process-mutex))

  stop: (lambda ()
    (create-sync:> self)
    (process-mutex<- nil)
    (when (notnil? process)
      (wake process)
      (join process)
      (process:! self nil))
    (<-process-mutex))

  update-function: (lambda (dt)) ;; Must be implemented by inheritors

  cleanup-function: (lambda ())

  deinitialize: (lambda ()
    (stop:> self))
})

(define color-pulser {
  proto*: Custom-Event-Dispatcher

  period: 30
  event-type: LightingType
  is-on: #t
  base-color: black-color
  pulse-color: white-color
  time-enabled: 0.0
  duration: 1.0
  
  compute-time: (lambda () (clamp (/ time-enabled (* 1000.0 duration)) 0.0 1.0))
  compute-percentage: (lambda (t) (* (- 1.0 (pow (- (* 2.0 t) 1.0) 2.0)) 100.0))
  compute-color: (lambda (p) (color-between base-color pulse-color p))

  run-update-side-effect: (lambda () (is-on:! self (not is-on)))
  run-finish-side-effect: (lambda () (is-on:! self #t))
  
  update-function: (lambda (dt)
    (let* ((time (compute-and-render-color)))
      (begin
        (time-enabled:! self (+ time-enabled dt))
        (when (>= time 1.0)
          (fork (lambda (proc) (stop:> self)))))))

  compute-and-render-color: (lambda ()
    (let* ((time (compute-time))
           (percentage (compute-percentage time))
           (color (compute-color percentage)))
      (begin
        (render-color color)
        time)))

  set-base-color: (lambda (c)
    (base-color:! self c)
    (compute-and-render-color))
    
  setup-and-enable: (lambda (c d)
    (stop)
    (pulse-color:! self c)
    (duration:! self d)
    (time-enabled:! self 0.0)
    (start)
    (compute-and-render-color))
})

           (color (static-color-frame->code (colorParam: (frame: data)))))
      (send color-pulser setup-and-enable: color duration))))
